Introduction

Sia Jiwoo, formerly known as simply Sia and also by her full name Park Jiwoo, is a South Korean singer, influencer and content creator under Just COLOR Studio and Starting House Entertainment. She was a former member of the cancelled trainee group Just COLOR.

She made her solo debut debut on October 7, 2022 with the digital single "Do It My Own Way (D.I.M.O.W)". She is also known for being a former contestant on the competitive reality show, MIXNINE.
